{"word":"εἰσαγγέλλω","slug":"εἰσαγγέλλω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>εἰσαγγέλλω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ελῶ</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to go in and announce</i> a person (<a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <el>εἰσαγγελεύς</el>) , <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to announce, report</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ἐσαγγελθέντων ὅτι . .</el> <i>information having been given that . .</i> , <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to impeach</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <el>εἰσαγγελία.</el> <p/></div>"}]}